summary: This is a calendar entry scheduling the start of jury selection (voir dire) for the Ghislaine Maxwell trial, set to begin on November 16, 2021, at the 40 Foley Courthouse. It was created and last modified on August 27, 2021.

events.title: Maxwell Jury Selection Voir Dire Start
events.description: Scheduled start date for the jury selection process (voir dire) in the trial of Ghislaine Maxwell.

keyFacts: The jury selection (voir dire) for Ghislaine Maxwell's trial was scheduled to begin on November 16, 2021.
The event was to take place at the 40 Foley Courthouse.
This calendar entry was created and last modified on August 27, 2021, indicating advanced planning for the trial proceedings.
